# === Secrets: never commit ===
# Real secrets live in Keychain / 1Password and are injected at apply time.
# NOTE: do NOT use a bare `*.local` — it also matches the XDG `.local/` dir and
# would exclude bin/.local/bin/*. Keep secret patterns specific.
*.local.sh
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.envrc
secrets/**/*.rendered
# Anything a tool might drop a token into:
**/.claude/settings.local.json

# === Generated / vendored (installed by bootstrap, not tracked) ===
tmux/.config/tmux/plugins/

# === OS / editor junk ===
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
tags

# === Build / logs ===
*.log
